Bundled battle animation data
-----------------------------
The file psclient/src/main/res/raw/battle_animations.json is generated by
build-tools/build_battle_animations.py from the Pokémon Showdown client source.
It is a data-only derivative (animation choreography: effect names, relative
coordinates, timings and transitions); no source code is redistributed.

  - The "moves" section is derived from
    play.pokemonshowdown.com/src/battle-animations-moves.ts, which its author
    dedicates to the public domain under CC0-1.0 (no conditions).

  - The "other" and "status" sections (and the on-device coordinate-projection
    math used to play them) are derived from
    play.pokemonshowdown.com/src/battle-animations.ts, the Pokémon Showdown
    battle animation engine, which is licensed under the MIT License:

